Effective Date: 2024 March 15

Our Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect information in relation to our mobile application, Discount Calculator. By using our app, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

Information Collection and Use:

Discount Calculator does not collect any personal information from its users. We do not require users to provide any personal information such as name, email address, phone number, or location data to use the app.


Third-Party Services:

Discount Calculator may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third-party sites or services. We encourage users to review the privacy policies of these third-party providers.

Changes to This Privacy Policy:

We reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes to the policy will be reflected in an updated version with a new effective date. We encourage users to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@msolutions.lk.

By using Discount Calculator, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms and conditions.
